main event: Unidentified flying object observed over Folsom, California, on multiple occasions.
interesting points: One witness described a bright white light traveling from the North to the Northeast for approximately 15-20 minutes., Multiple reports indicate objects observed at high altitudes moving rapidly., The first report suggested it was probably a satellite passing overhead., A citizen reported seeing a round object illuminated with white light hovering silently in the area., Two witnesses observed a round, bright object with flashing lights for about 10 seconds.
sighted object: Unidentified flying object (described as bright light and round with flashing lights)
witness description: Witnesses included military personnel and local citizens who described the object moving rapidly and exhibiting unusual characteristics.
